description:
It's been over 3 weeks since the tragic helicopter crash that claimed the life of Kobe Bryant and his young daughter and still officials are without answers as to what all caused the incident. But even stranger are the cases of his death being predicted in the media and all of the occult connections and strange coincidences swirling around his sudden demise. On this special Off The Cuff episode, we ask what really happened to Kobe Bryant?
